    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215665>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Namalycastis occulta n. sp. A. Anterior end, dorsal view (insert: close-up of antennae). B. Posterior end, dorsal view. C. Jaw, dorsal view (insert: tip of jaw, frontal view). D. Chaetiger 3, right parapodium, frontal view. E. Chaetiger 36, right parapodium, frontal view. F. Chaetiger 88, right parapodium, frontal view. G. Supra-acicular heterogomph falciger, chaetiger 36. H. Sub-acicular heterogomph falciger, chaetiger 36. I. Sub-acicular heterogomph falciger, chaetiger 3 (insert: distal tip). J. Sub-acicular heterogomph spiniger, chaetiger 36 (insert: blade tip). K. Supra-acicular sesquigomph spiniger, chaetiger 36. A – B, D – K. from holotype ECOSUR P- 0151; C. from paratype ECOSUR P- 0152. Scale bars: A, B, 0.25 mm; C, D, E, F, 0.05 mm; G, H, I, J, K, 0.01 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215665/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.215666>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Namalycastis occulta n. sp. A. Entire, incomplete specimen, dorsal view, arrow indicates first oocyte. B. Oocytes from posterior chaetigers. C. Chaetiger from mid body, cross-ection (in: intestine, oc: oocyte). A, from specimen ECOSUR P- 2650; B – C, from specimen ECOSUR P- 2650. Scale bars: A, 0.5 mm; B, C, 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/215666/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

